gomodel:SYNGO_2493  a    owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment     "Rationale: immunogold labelling of GABAC R in retinal Bipolar cell terminals.\n\n19/01/2021 Dnyanada: Immunoreaction product is localised on the presynaptic side (represented by an asterisk). \"integral component...\" was chosen based on transmembrane topology as represented in G1SEE5 (G1SEE5_RABIT).\n\nA polyclonal antiserum raised against amino acid residues 16-171 of the rat r1 subunit that recognizes the subunits r1, r2, and r3 of the GABAC receptor was used. The antibody used is not paralog-specific.. Experimental description: Rabbit: Retinae of adult New Zealand white rabbits (2.5-3.5 kg) were investigated." , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" ;
        lego:modelstate  "production" ;
        dc:contributor   "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9425-2935" ;
        dc:date          "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title         "SYNGO_CC_2493" ;
        pav:providedBy   "https://syngo.vu.nl" .

